      <t:body>
         <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><t:ab>በስመ፡ … ድርሳን፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ኢጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ሥሩግ፡ በእንተ፡ አብርሃም፡ አቡነ፡ አርከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</t:ab></t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="subscriptio explicit" xml:id="colophon"><t:ab>
               ወይረሲ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ማኅደሮ፡ ለአቡነ፡ አባ፡ ሰላማ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ደርገ፡ አሜን፨ 
               ለዝንቱ፡ ድርሳን፡ ዘአጽሐፎ፡ አቡነ፡ አባ፡
               ሰላማ፡ ጳጳስ፡ ርቱዓ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ እምዐረቢ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዚአሁ፡ ለግዕዝ፤ ይተሉ፡ ዝየ፡ ተጽሕፎ፡ ዘይቤ፡ አባ፡
               አትናስዮስ። <t:note>quoted after <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESgbi002">GBI-002</t:ref></t:note> <t:note>Subscriptio ascribing the translation
                  of the homily (from Arabic into Gǝʿǝz) to Metropolitan <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8387SalamaI">ʾabbā Salāma</t:persName>;
                  besides, the authorship of the work is here attributed to <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2209Athanasi">Athanasius</t:persName>
                  (Bishop of Alexandria from 328 to 373; cp. EAE I, 392)</t:note>
            </t:ab></t:div>
            
         </t:div>
         
         
         
      </t:body>
